3	// compare_adapter.go provides comparison, quorum, and benchmark execution
4	// helpers for DDx. The compare/quorum/benchmark execution logic accepts a
5	// run-function closure so production callers can drive arms via the agent
6	// service (RunViaService) while legacy Runner-bound tests can keep using
7	// Runner.Run.
8	//
9	// The Runner.RunCompare/Runner.RunQuorum/Runner.RunBenchmark wrappers below
10	// remain in place for test scaffolding only; production code should call
11	// RunCompareViaService, RunQuorumViaService, and RunBenchmarkViaService.
12	//
13	// Phase 5h migration (ddx-bfff4bc7): Runner shim methods deleted; production
14	// calls use ViaService variants directly. Tests use RunCompareWith/RunQuorumWith
15	// with an injected RunFunc.
